question:
\[f(n) = \left\{
\begin{array}{cl}
\lfloor n \rfloor & \text{ if }n \geq 4, \\
\lceil n \rceil & \text{ if } n < 4.
\end{array}
\right.\]일 때, $f\left(\frac{\pi}{3}\right) + f(\sqrt{45}) + f(8^{2/3})$를 구하시오.

response:
\begin{align*}
f\left(\frac{\pi}{3}\right) + f(\sqrt{45}) + f(8^{2/3}) &= \lceil \frac{\pi}{3} \rceil + \lfloor \sqrt{45} \rfloor + \lfloor 8^{2/3} \rfloor \\
&= 2 + 6 + 4 \\
&= \boxed{12}.
\end{align*}

